to pull that off. What do you say?

33:59.252 --> 34:01.766
Why don't we just see
what the future holds.

34:06.452 --> 34:08.522
Would that have satisfied her?

34:08.891 --> 34:09.927
What's that?

34:10.012 --> 34:11.081
A judgeship.

34:11.172 --> 34:14.482
I wonder if a judgeship
would've satisfied Carolyn Polhemus.

34:29.411 --> 34:30.367
Rusty!

34:30.452 --> 34:33.603
Come say hello to Carolyn Polhemus.
Have you met?

34:34.331 --> 34:35.731
