37:10.532 --> 37:14.730
You think I got this job because
I fucked some fat-cat friend of Raymond's.

37:18.212 --> 37:19.611
Look, it's late....

37:22.572 --> 37:24.961
Come on, I'll drive you to your ferry.

37:28.212 --> 37:30.362
This is not the way to the ferry.

37:30.772 --> 37:32.524
I want you to meet somebody.

37:32.612 --> 37:34.728
Wendell, this is Rusty Sabich.

37:37.412 --> 37:40.006
He's a very important man in our office.

37:40.252 --> 37:43.050
He's going to help me
when we go to court.

37:44.012 --> 37:46.242
Remember what I told you about court?

37:46.532 --> 37:47.567
Yeah.

37:48.292 --> 37:49.725
Now, tell me.

37:50.772 --> 37:52.967
There's a judge and some nice people.

37:53.052 --> 37:54.849
They're called a jury.

37:55.252 --> 37:57.527
And you're gonna ask me questions.

37:58.012 --> 37:59.240
About what?

38:02.732 --> 38:04.450
About what happened.

38:04.972 --> 38:05.927
When?

38:06.612 --> 38:08.045
When I got hurt.

38:08.492 --> 38:10.369
What else did I tell you?

38:11.292 --> 38:14.090
