38:14.772 --> 38:17.889
...the judge and the nice people
will protect me...

38:18.132 --> 38:20.600
...and Mommy wouldn't hurt me anymore.

38:21.332 --> 38:23.209
Do you think you can do that?

38:23.292 --> 38:25.408
Answer my questions in court?

38:26.092 --> 38:28.287
And tell what Mommy did to you?

38:31.172 --> 38:32.764
I think you can.

38:33.132 --> 38:34.850
Mommy will be there.

38:35.812 --> 38:38.770
She can't hurt you.
She can't even talk to you.

38:39.412 --> 38:41.323
You'll be completely safe.

38:43.772 --> 38:45.091
You promise?

38:46.812 --> 38:48.131
I promise.

38:56.492 --> 38:58.164
His father got to him last night.

38:58.252 --> 39:01.289
Told him God would put him in hell
if he testified against his mother.

39:01.372 --> 39:02.407
He's terrified.

39:02.492 --> 39:05.723
If you're not ready, we'll ask the judge
for a couple more days.

39:05.812 --> 39:06.767
No.

39:06.892 --> 39:09.452
We've got to do it now
or we'll lose him for good.

39:09.532 --> 39:12.729
Your mommy took you to the hospital
because you were hurt.

39:13.252 --> 39:15.129
What part of you was hurt?

39:15.772 --> 39:16.887
My head.

39:17.852 --> 39:19.444
How was it hurt?

39:23.732 --> 39:26.166
Wendell, how did you hurt your head?

39:29.532 --> 39:31.124
